_sText:
This is my first bhop map I've made, so enjoy! :D

Includes:

- 10 Levels
- Bonus
- Spawn
- Gravity Changer at end
- Level pick at end
- 6 Secret nades (with trails)
- Deagle and Awp with trails

The secret nades are in spawn, level 2, level 5, level 7, level 8, and level 10.
Have fun finding them!

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

UPDATES:

- Fixed ladder glitch where u lose gravity.
- Added "Super Low Grav" at end (0.1).
- Fixed some textures and placements of platforms.
- Changed trails on deagle and awp.
- Decreased the speed of the platforms on lvl 9 (1/3).
- Optimized some parts better.
- Added 2 secret nades.
